# _sys/boot scope 25 — path-based router (/mcp → mcp-server).
#
# Routes /mcp and /mcp/* to the mcp-server stack (a JSON-RPC MCP server
# written entirely in txcl). See route-default.txcl for why this is
# EMIT, at scope 25, and guarded on `@route.to == ""`.
#
# @ is sugar for ._txc.
WHEN @route.to == "" && @src == "http" && @web.req.url.path =~ /^\/mcp(\/.*)?$/
  EMIT @route.tenant = "default",
       @route.stack = "mcp-server",
       @route.to = "mcp-server/0"
